Schuler is a member of the Rutgers Hall of Distinguished Alumni.
Meteor Vineyard[edit]
Meteor Vineyard is a 22-acre (89,000 m2) property located in the Coombsville agricultural area of the Napa Valley AVA. It was established in 1998 by former America Online Inc. Chairman and Chief Executive Barry M. Schuler and his wife, Tracy Strong Schuler. Meteor Vineyard is located at the southeast end of the Napa Valley, near the San Francisco Bay.
