The Dark Side of Equity Crowdfunding


If your company can be cash-flow positive with one round of financing, equity crowd funding might work for you. But if your idea is truly huge, you may prefer to have professionals on your side. Here's why






 By Barry Schuler


Barry Schuler is managing director for DFJ Growth and the former chairman and CEO of America Online. He is credited with being one of the pioneers of the modern Internet.
@BSchuler 


Managing Director, DFJ Growth@BSchuler 










8 COMMENTS
























